data.description: Beautifully appointed one story cottage style home w/ proximity to Loop 1604, SH 151, & Loop 410. Living area is spacious and inviting w/ vaulted ceiling and stained wood beam, cozy painted brick fireplace, and large opening to dining. Neutral paint palette (2022) compliments wood-look flooring throughout (2022) w/ slate tile in bathrooms. Galley kitchen remodeled in 2022 and boasts custom cabinetry w/ recessed panel cabinets and decorative pulls, stone counters, subway tile splash, and stainless appliances. Recent improvements include window and HVAC replacement (2022), updated lighting - decorative, recessed, & fans - and installed water softener (2023). "French style" doors lead to the patio slab perfect for entertaining with surrounding updates like exterior paint (2023), privacy fence (2023), garage door (2022), and landscaping (2023). Shed provides additional storage options.
